  "instructions": [
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together olive oil, jalape\t6\u00074\u0019 oil, garlic, cumin, and chili powder.",
    "In a large skillet, warm the tortillas over medium heat for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "Grill the lemongrass stalks over medium heat for 3-4 minutes on each side, or until slightly charred.",
    "To assemble the tacos, place a warmed tortilla on a flat surface, then top with a piece of grilled lemongrass, a sprinkle of feta cheese (if using), and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Serve immediately with ssam-wraps on the side for wrapping.",
    "Repeat with remaining ingredients.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!",
    "Garnish with additional lemongrass, feta cheese, and lime juice, if desired."
